    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114430/extras/8a70104a126eba1e44a4ee46e3a72a8b.avif?t=1764953687\" width=620 height=100 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114430/extras/1f13aa731ad1609936175ae2580be62a.avif?t=1764953687\" width=350 height=100 /></span><br>You must build a big city in a Cyber ​​/ SCI-FI universe composed of several districts to grow the population through various simple actions.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114430/extras/758225367c562522cddeb521eeddcf4b.avif?t=1764953687\" width=350 height=100 /></span><br>Made by a lone developper, ACHIEVEMENTS CITY is a unique chill game fast and easy to complete.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2>- 7 different keyboard and 3 mouse actions<br>- See the different districts being built in front of you, control the risks of multiple innovations, activate aerial signals or even set up an electrical path.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Style</strong></h2>- A simple and minimalist decor that will immerse you in a Cyber ​​/ SCI-FI world growing with each of your actions.<br>- Simple, short, relaxed, without the fuss and above all without Game Over, let yourself be carried away by its bewitching atmosphere.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114430/extras/025a968594040b418756981364d3d3bf.avif?t=1764953687\" width=350 height=100 /></span>",
